{"tid":2274300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"復課難適應 中學生壓力爆煲","createTime":"2020-11-06T10:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T11:09:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf75b275c487815655cd73c7f99ef33f17a6ef5f","tid":2274300,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/QUIV2GKPI5BUBMVMHQDXV7IHCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FQUIV2GKPI5BUBMVMHQDXV7IHCM%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9kbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=2b0e16d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FQUIV2GKPI5BUBMVMHQDXV7IHCM%2F&h=3373de12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/QUIV2GKPI5BUBMVMHQDXV7IHCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n復課難適應 中學生壓力爆煲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aq9nkFUli6oy6IVqBBRHBfKVnzQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TUA4RAZXANBJDLDY4ECRRLEEYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Faq9nkFUli6oy6IVqBBRHBfKVnzQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTUA4RAZXANBJDLDY4ECRRLEEYQ.jpg&h=49f4c6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港青年協會調查發現，不少學生難以適應開學環境，逾半受訪學生壓力指數處於偏高水平。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫情下莘莘學子幾經波折，終在9月底恢復面授課堂。香港青年協會調查發現，不少學生難以適應開學環境，逾半受訪學生壓力指數處於偏高水平，比例創十年新高，亦較去年增10.5%。學生最擔憂的事情依次為「要應付測驗考試」、「成績未如理想」及「休息時間減少」，亦有逾七成學生認為防疫工作比追趕學習進度重要，甚至不介意取消陸運會等活動以減風險。<br />\n<br />\n青協於今年9至10月期間，以。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七成受訪者珍惜回校上學<br />\n<br />\n感焦慮的學生橫跨不同年級。青協透露，有臨近應考文憑試的學生，為追上停課及網課期間的進度，壓力爆煲致發噩夢及失眠；亦有學生因停課與同儕關係生疏，慘被杯葛，萌退學念頭。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，亦有近七成受訪學生表示會更珍惜回校上學的日子。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z0-xr5LWFEbV3TiQCQdx9GAWLuk=/829x491/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FKBESUNZDNEYRAFFPZQR7RFZZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz0-xr5LWFEbV3TiQCQdx9GAWLuk%3D%2F829x491%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFKBESUNZDNEYRAFFPZQR7RFZZM.jpg&h=288563a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2b3429f3f11fbff299e6ca025a5feca2c3811d0","tid":2274300,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"學建退"},{"pid":"d0843ca31cf66ea331061072243b6cd409de66ed","tid":2274300,"uid":222966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"校內考試？wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考好dse咪得。依家應該抱住返去同同學仔玩既心態，而唔係d濕9考試"}]}